'''劉易斯與克拉克河'''（{{lang-en|Lewis and Clark River}}）是{{tsl|en|Youngs River|揚斯河}}的支流，位於[[美國|美國]][[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]]內。河流長約{{convert|20|mi|km}}，面積為{{convert|62|mi2|km2}}<ref name="WBD"/>。

== 流向 ==
河流發源自俄勒岡州[[克拉特索普縣|克拉特索普縣]]的{{tsl|en|Saddle Mountain (Clatsop County, Oregon)|馬鞍山 (俄勒岡州)|馬鞍山}}內<ref name="Hussey's Report">{{Cite web |url = http://npshistory.com/publications/lewi/suggested-historical-area.pdf |title = Suggetsed Historical Area Report - Fort Clatsop Site, Oregon |last = Hussey |first = John A. |date = 1957-04-10 |publisher = National Park Service |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190117121915/http://npshistory.com/publications/lewi/suggested-historical-area.pdf |archivedate = 2019-01-17 }}</ref>。河水會往西北方流，並在錫賽德市東面與劉易斯與克拉克河南汊合流<ref name="Hussey's Report"/>。之後河水會往北方流，流經{{tsl|en|Lewis and Clark National and State Historical Parks|劉易斯與克拉克國家歷史公園}}，最終在{{tsl|en|Jeffers Garden, Oregon|傑弗斯花園}}附近與揚斯河匯合<ref name="Hussey's Report"/>。

== 歷史 ==
1803年，[[路易斯安那購地|美國向法國購買法屬路易斯安那]]。當時的美國總統[[湯瑪斯·傑佛遜|湯瑪斯·傑佛遜]]為了探明[[密蘇里河|密蘇里河]]及其主要支流，發起了由探險家[[梅里韋瑟·路易斯|梅里韋瑟·路易斯]]及[[威廉·克拉克_(探險家)|威廉·克拉克]]帶領的遠征活動，史稱「[[路易斯與克拉克遠征|路易斯與克拉克遠征]]」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://missouririverwatertrail.org/river-history/river-lewis-and-clark |title = The River of Lewis and Clark |author = Missouri River Water Trail |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170401004159/https://missouririverwatertrail.org/river-history/river-lewis-and-clark |archivedate = 2017-04-01 }}</ref>。1805年11月30日，路易斯及克拉克等人在探索揚斯灣地區時發現了這條河流<ref name="Lewis and Clark River, Oregon">{{Cite web |url = http://columbiariverimages.com/Regions/Places/lewis_clark_river.html |title = Lewis and Clark River, Oregon |author = ColumbiaRiverImages.com |date = 2010 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191223011455/http://columbiariverimages.com/Regions/Places/lewis_clark_river.html |archivedate = 2019-12-23 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://lewisandclarkjournals.unl.edu/item/lc.jrn.1805-11-30 |title = The Journals of the Lewis and Clark Expedition |last = Lewis |first = Meriwether |last2 = Clark |first2 = William |date = 1805-11-30 |publisher = University of Nebraska Press |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200819055629/https://lewisandclarkjournals.unl.edu/item/lc.jrn.1805-11-30 |archivedate = 2020-08-19 }}</ref>。同年12月，為了準備過冬，遠征隊員在河流附近建設了{{tsl|en|Fort Clatsop|克拉特索普堡}}，並在聖誕節前夕遷入<ref name="Lewis and Clark River, Oregon"/>。1806年1月28日，路易斯在其日記上紀錄了克拉特索普印第安人把這條河流稱為「內圖爾河」（Ne-tul River）<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://lewisandclarkjournals.unl.edu/item/lc.jrn.1806-01-28 |title = The Journals of the Lewis and Clark Expedition |last = Lewis |first = Meriwether |last2 = Clark |first2 = William |date = 1806-01-28 |publisher = University of Nebraska Press |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200819061032/https://lewisandclarkjournals.unl.edu/item/lc.jrn.1806-01-28 |archivedate = 2020-08-19 }}</ref>。在結束遠征活動時，路易斯及克拉克還把克拉特索普堡和其他家具贈送予酋長科博韋（Coboway）<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.lewis-clark.org/article/2816 |title = Lewis and Clark River - Coast Range Winter |last = Mussulman |first = Joseph |publisher = Discovering Lewis & Clark |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213062332/https://www.lewis-clark.org/article/2816 |archivedate = 2020-02-13 }}</ref>。

1792年，[[英國|英國]][[英國皇家海軍|皇家海軍]]軍官[[喬治·溫哥華|喬治·溫哥華]]所率領的探險隊經過這條河流，其中一名隊員{{tsl|en|William Robert Broughton|威廉·羅伯特·布勞頓}}卻錯誤地把其認為是揚斯河，導致後來很多學者都認為布勞頓所指的這條「揚斯河」等於同樣位於克拉特索普縣的揚斯河<ref name="Youngs River, Oregon">{{Cite web |url = http://columbiariverimages.com/Regions/Places/youngs_river.html |title = Youngs River, Oregon |author = ColumbiaRiverImages.com |date = 2010 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-19 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200117125026/http://columbiariverimages.com/Regions/Places/youngs_river.html |archivedate = 2020-01-17 }}</ref>。

1925年前，河流名稱仍然沿用克拉特索普印第安人的稱謂「內圖爾河」{{sfn|White|Findlay|1999|p=4, 19}}。後來為了紀念梅里韋瑟·路易斯及威廉·克拉克，河流的名稱被改為「劉易斯與克拉克河」{{sfn|White|Findlay|1999|p=4, 19}}。

